				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				1. PoD is level 50. Plain and simple<BR>
2. About a week ago, he was kited by two magicians on rodcet nife who wanted to try out the new dual wield option for pets. It took them 15 minutes to kill him.<BR>
3. The PoD is a cleric. He casts retribution, which is a 514 dmg dd, level 44.<BR>
4. He has 32,000 hp, just like Cazic, Innoruuk, and most likely Veeshan when she is finally sighted, and eventually killed.<BR>
5. He can be kited. He does hit for 350 dmg and needs a magic weapon to be hit.<BR>
6. He casts complete heal when he is down to about 10% health. Luckily, the magician pets interrupted him making it so the two magicians would not be slaughtered.<BR>
<BR>
If you want proof of his items, contact Flaimer from Luna Imperium. He has the robe, and the other magician has the staff.<BR>
<BR>
P.S. The PoD drops high level words/runes. They took his robe and staff but left rest on him. I got lucky enough to loot Words of Crippling Force, for the level 49 necromancer spell Paralyzing Earth.<BR>
<BR>
